data.title: Watch The Joke (1969) Full Movie Online
data.meta_description: Where to watch The Joke (1969) starring Josef Somr, Jana Dítětová, Luděk Munzar and directed by Jaromil Jireš.
data.text: In the 1950's, Ludvik Jahn was expelled from the Communist Party and the University by his fellow students, because of a politically incorrect note he sent to his girlfriend. Fifteen years later, he tries to get his revenge by seducing Helena, the wife of one of his accusers.
